  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Create the Sides",
      "body": "Attach the two 1x3 sides @ 32\" to the two 1x3 sides @ 16\" using 1 1/4\" Kreg screws.\nPlease note that these measurements were all created to fit the standard boot tray I have. You may need to alter the measurements to suit yours.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/a40f5d95a70cf194.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Prepare Slats",
      "body": "Cut all 13 1x2 slats down to 16\" and add 2 pocket holes on each end.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/bc837048acdc6f08.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Measure Your Boot Tray",
      "body": "All of the instructions for this boot tray cover are made and measured to suit my standard boot tray which is 29 3/4\" x 14 3/4\".\nPlease note you may need to alter the measurements to suit your project.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/43750d9d3ad68acb.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Attach Slats",
      "body": "Attach each slat with 1 1/4\" pocket screws. Use a scrap piece of 1x2 to space the 13 slats evenly.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/54356fe358efcfbf.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Finish as Desired",
      "body": "Due to wet shoes frequently landing on this wood, you will want to treat it with polyurethane for protection.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/6298d59c21d3e27a.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Admire the Beauty",
      "body": "Something about all those evenly spaced lines is beautiful, isn't it? :)",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/f9dc1826c34710af.webp"
    }
  ],
